Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西怪怪的  我不知為啥有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視中正在播放的  是跟我一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥我正支持著正處於落後的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又不知為啥覺得差不多春日要搞點事出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合  老老實實地過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一句話都沒說上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:00:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說帶東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳裝  還有足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定要騎自行車來  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我連一句話都沒說上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像又知道春日打算要說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說  是感覺之前好像出現過完全相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的「既視感」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就這樣繳槍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿點幹勁出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這準備的架勢來看也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天當然要有夏天的樣子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我們是騎自行車去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也騎來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  自行車只有你和我的兩輛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  阿虛  可不能輸給古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  立即出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你們兩個趕緊停好車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿虛  接下來是要玩啊  你怎麼就筋疲力盡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的錯啊  誰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這消毒液的氣味  真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽哦比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮同學  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺歡樂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很歡樂的情景  還真讓人感到和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得  涼宮同學也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打個電話過來  單方面地說有事就掛的邀請方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能說得上是常識性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那點事  要我說根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為從初春開始就發生了太多事情 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得有點神經質了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希  我們再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼春日會選這樣一個地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼春日會選這樣一個地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  然後春日說了這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個就是我的團員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼他們都會聽的  所以隨便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這種事也常有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既視感什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘不多的暑假該如何度過的預定表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然發現  暑假只剩下兩個星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要趕快地去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在不到兩週內搞完這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠有什麼想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撈…金…魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近什麼地方有盂蘭盆會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙火匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我給錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  其實也沒有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近如何  精神好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打攪你了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  為什麼我會去和長門搭腔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  將我的懶覺奪走的又是春日的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是說找到盂蘭盆會的會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  地點似乎是市民運動場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  今天你又是最後一個  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了  我們大伙一起去買浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日進了女裝的大賣場之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自為朝比奈學姐和長門挑選了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後毫不客氣地衝進了試衣間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們等了大約一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人終於出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  太可愛了  真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐  轉過來！轉過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這麼熱鬧真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆會啊  真虧得能聚集起這麼多人…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  怎麼又是這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有你想要玩的撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撈個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩吧  來一決高下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個來  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  長門  你對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥有種受她照顧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那種程度的我來買就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那麼多  就只要了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一個的話沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那面具哪裡弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來玩煙火吧  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  雖然極力想要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情卻讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  明天是捉昆蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼嘛  那種程度的作業有三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three days！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾掉再玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙腦子這麼好  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天對於人的參數調整還真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  明天去捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的蟲子最多的那個人  怎麼好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就把團長的權力讓給他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是蟲子的話什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是個讓人有種「連這也是啊」的感覺的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰就在這大晴天下進行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說大家都在努力奮鬥  可應該說不出所料還是說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  還是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它們一條生路  以後說不定會來報恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬來了到底能為我們做些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點打開了盒子的潘多拉的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  我們在一無所知的情況下被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始在超市的門口兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這待遇差算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就為了這種東西累死累活地幹活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這放在社團室做紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  奪去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  有非常不好的事情…這樣下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會這個時候跟朝比奈學姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點情況  你能現在就過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了  朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  事情是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在永久地重複著同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你滿面春光地把那種非現實的話說出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你知道自己在說什麼嗎  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  相當清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和朝比奈學姐談了下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊  然後你好回去了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:15:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後意識到最近這裡時間的流動出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該說是朝比奈學姐的功績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託她的福我也確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確信什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經重複體驗同樣的時間許多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才就聽你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說應該是八月十七日到三十一日之間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於一個沒有盡頭的暑假的正當中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在確實是暑假…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法結束的Endless Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個世界裡  九月一日之後的時間全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要誰相信那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被困在那個叫什麼封鎖空間裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的時間被分割開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四時整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  全人類的記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也會重置  會重頭再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是關於時間這個那個了的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…既然未來人也混進來了  那我覺得也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這件事和朝比奈學姐沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是涼宮同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然本人沒有這個自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡什麼地方總在想著暑假不要結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊  難道留著什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她是想著暑假還有什麼事情剩下沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個\N會把一些莫名其妙的事情展開到大宇宙規模的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了這個的話  就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就覺得  你好像樂在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知你是不是也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近頻繁發生的既視感之迷終於解開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來  那只能理解為是由於記憶重置而散落下來的殘渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道說全世界的人都感覺得到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣  我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙多少有一點意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  別說是既視感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該有一個人保存著所有輪迴中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說也該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問下  這重複現在到底是第幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是第15527次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你在說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那話是認真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的次數  我們全都在重複同樣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527次中沒有去盂蘭盆會的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的這兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂蘭盆會而沒有撈金魚的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9052次  其內容有6個模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了發放氣球  還有搬貨物  做收銀員  發送傳單…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15527次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門她這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上兩週的話就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是595年的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長的時間僅她一個人能夠好好地保留著記憶  無數次無數次地重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你到底到現在為止都是以什麼樣的心情度過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天是觀測天體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是長門的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天體望遠鏡由古泉準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類第一次踏上火星的時候  一定會從暗處跑出來歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歡迎來到火星」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的話  也能順利解決了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試下這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面突然抱住涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳邊輕語「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由誰來做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你沒有適合的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I…I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不要  我要擺脫這種支配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來做怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的了  我做這角色還不夠格  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓涼宮同學增加無謂的混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之後去了打擊中心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝比奈學姐說出來之前就注意到了這輪迴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的工作是觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒濤般的暑假活動消化體制還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會  釣蝦虎魚大會  試膽  電影連看後是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在活動來活動去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我覺得春日應該不會這樣就滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此  也沒有什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣終於來到了  八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣課題就如實地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也就這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假已經做了好多事了  已經很充實了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還沒有滿足才對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天在社團教室再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  春…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還前所未有地強烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能讓春日回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重複了一萬幾千次的兩星期又要陷入永遠循環的窘境了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我該做什麼呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的話裡應該有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  我想不起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.07,0:23:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業  還沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎麼都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重複的話  作業做了也沒意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天來不來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  也只能交給那時的我來處理了吧
